This universal bed system has a fixed base system that allows the production of beams with a base up to 80 cm. The tensioning head system has relaxation cylinders and the corresponding tensioning equipment, for 12- and 15-mm diameter strands. This system will allow our client to start developing the market for industrial and logistics warehouses in the Monterrey region, in addition to producing beams for bridges. Along with the universal prestressing bed system, MOLDTECH has supplied a modular length “Delta” beam mould, which will allow the customer to produce “Delta” beams up to 34 meters in length. These beams will be used for the construction of industrial and logistics warehouses. About Moldtech It was established in 1986 to become a worldwide reference in the precast concrete sector by providing comprehensive technological solutions in high quality equipment and machinery. Their expertise is based on moulds for columns, stairs, slabs, casting beds, beams, box culverts, new jersey barriers and both fixed and tilting tables. The company design, develop and install integral production systems, adapted to the needs of the client, which respect the highest European standards of quality, production and safety. Their clients come from more than 40 countries, in America, Europe, Africa, Asia and Oceania endorse their trajectory. 